          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">Finches (from <em>Dust</em>, published by Dalkey Archive Press) <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue7/arkadii_dragomoschenko/bio.php" class="link3">Arkadii Dragomoschenko</a></span><BR>
          Translated from the Russian by <a href="../../issue7/shushan_avagyan/bio.php" class="link3">Shushan Avagyan</a> &amp; <a href="../../issue7/ana_lucic/bio.php" class="link3">Ana Lucic</a>  
